      <view class="row">4、购买成功后不可退，请合理安排出行时间</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- <>图文详情 -->
  <view class="pro-simliar mt20 pad20 bg--fff">
    <view class="tit">图文详情</view>
    <view class="cnt">
      <view class="row">别墅套票-翠屏雅苑两卧/三卧+自助早餐+魔术表演（逢周二停演）+4成人次日自助早餐</view>
      <view class="row">别墅套票-翠屏雅苑两卧/三卧+自助早餐+魔术表演（逢周二停演）+4成人次日自助早餐</view>
      <view class="row">4.29-5.1：两卧加价600元/套，三卧加价900元/套</view>
      <view class="row"><image class="max__img" src="../../../images/114.png" mode="widthFix"></image></view>
      <view class="row"><image class="max__img" src="../../../images/hotel__img-detail.jpg" mode="widthFix"></image></view>
      <view class="row"><image class="max__img" src="../../../images/swiper__mall-img01.jpg" mode="widthFix"></image></view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- <>详细地址 -->
  <view class="pro-address mt20 pad20 bg--fff">
    <view class="flexbox flex-alignc">
      <view class="addr clamp1 flex1">详细地址：广东省广州市越秀区东湖寺右新马路  广东省广州市越秀区东湖寺右新马路</view>
      <label class="ico-hotel i3" style="background-image: url(../../../images/icons-hotel.png);"></label>
    </view>
  </view>

  <!-- <>底部固定按钮 -->
  <view class="pro-footinfo">
    <view class="bottomfixed">
      <view class="inner flexbox flex-alignc">
